description:
Matt and Stak are joined by music executive Dame Dash on the latest episode of ATS. Dash discusses co-founding Roc-A-Fella with Jay-Z and their relationship. Plus, he talks the legacies of Biggie & Tupac and how Kayne is his Michael Jackson.
